msgid "Telegram bot options"
msgstr "Telegram bot options"

msgid "Status"
msgstr "Status"

msgid "Bot is connected"
msgstr "Bot is connected"

msgid "Bot is not connected"
msgstr "Bot is not connected"

msgid "Telegram bot info for add"
msgstr "To set up and connect the bot, follow these steps in the Telegram app:<br>1. <u>Find the bot</u>: Enter <b>@%1$s</b> in the global search bar and select it from the results list.<br>2. <u>Start the dialog</u>: Click the 'Start' button at the bottom of the screen or send the /start command.<br>3. <u>Activate features</u>: send to bot this message <b>%2$s</b><br><br>After this, the bot should respond to you in accordance with its settings."

msgid "Bad init"
msgstr "Incorrect activation string. Open (refresh) the board configuration page in your profile and copy the entire activation string (highlighted in bold) here."

msgid "Setting information"
msgstr "You can configure this bot in your board profile."

msgid "Bot is connected, set it up"
msgstr "Bot is connected, configure it in your profile on the board."

msgid "Delete telebot"
msgstr "Disable this bot"

msgid "Delete telebot info"
msgstr "Once you've disabled this bot, you can delete the chat with it (but don't block it) in the Telegram app."
